collection.name: Swampverse
collection.description:
**OpenSea item count is incorrect** - there are only 7,450 Swampers remaining, the rest have been sent to a burn address. Burning is still live. Count updated April 30.

Join the swamp where your NFT itself doubles as membership to a community, alpha, merchandise, events & P2E game's which are yet to be released. Our goal is to help anyone break their way into the NFT world successfully while having fun. 


Other Collections: [Swampverse: Creatures](https://opensea.io/collection/swampverse-creatures)
- [Swampverse: Mini Drops](https://opensea.io/collection/swampverse-mini-drops)
